nodes.text: This individual was a member of the Rebel Alliance. When her father, a librarian, was captured by CompForce during a police action, she led a squad of Rebels in liberating the both her father and the prisoners. She also took a prisoner of her own, the CompForcer Zevulon Veers, who professed his wish to defect to the Alliance. Initially she was distrustful of Veers, but was won over by her father's testimony after Veers gave medical aid to the wounded librarian.
